illiams\n| title2          = New Forms\n| note2           = featuring Bahamadia\n| writer2         = {{hlist|Williams|Reed|Southey}}\n| length2         = 7:45\n| title4          = Let's Get It On\n| length4         = 6:57\n| writer4         = Williams\n| title6          = Matter of Fact\n| writer6         = Williams\n| length6         = 4:05\n| title7          = Mad Cat\n| writer7         = Williams\n| length7         = 4:56\n| title5          = Share the Fall\n| note5           = Full Vocal Mix\n| writer5         = {{hlist|Williams|Onallee|Kausman|Thompson}}\n| length5         = 6:13\n| title9          = Beatbox\n| writer9         = {{hlist|Williams|Southey}}\n| length9         = 1:09\n| title8          = Morse Code\n| writer8         = Williams\n| length8         = 6:58\n| title10         = Destination\n| writer10        = {{hlist|Williams|Onallee|Watt|Thorn}}\n| length10        = 8:12\n}}\n\n{{tracklist\n| collapsed       = yes\n| headline        = 5x vinyl\n| title1          = Hi-Potent\n| writer1         = Williams\n| length1         = 6:53\n| title2          = Trust Me\n| writer2         = Williams\n| length2         = 6:26\n| title3          = Change My Life\n| writer3         = Williams\n| length3         = 8:27\n| title4          = Share the Fall\n| writer4         = {{hlist|Williams|Onallee|Kausman|Thompson}}\n| length4         = 6:26\n| title5          = Down\n| writer5         = {{hlist|Williams|Kausman}}\n| length5         = 6:51\n| title6          = Jazz\n| writer6         = {{hlist|Williams|Southey}}\n| length6         = 6:04\n| title7          = Hot Stuff\n| writer7         = {{hlist|Williams|Thompson}}\n| length7         = 6:32\n| title8          = Ballet Dance\n| writer8         = {{hlist|Williams|Kausman}}\n| length8         = 6:41\n| title9          = Heroes\n| note9           = Album Version\n| writer9         = {{hlist|Williams|Onallee}}\n| length9         = 6:35\n| title10         = Digital\n| writer10        = {{hlist|Williams|Onallee}}\n| le